<section id="about" class="section" aria-label="About Black62 Commodities">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="two-col">
      <div class="reveal">
        <p class="eyebrow">About Us</p>
        <h2 class="display-2 silver">From Tsogang Brands to Black62 Commodities</h2>
        <div class="prose">
          <p>Black62 Commodities is the new identity of Tsogang Brands (Pty) Ltd — a South African trading and bulk logistics business with a decade of operating heritage and over twenty years of combined management experience across mining, energy and agriculture.</p>
          <p>Our rebrand reflects our sharper focus: physical commodities trading in coal, chrome and animal feed, supported by our own 62-ton abnormal heavy-haul fleet. We work with reputable producers, hauliers and end-users to move material at scale, on schedule, and with full compliance.</p>
          <p>We operate across the three sectors that matter to South Africa's economy — energy, mining and agriculture — and bring the same discipline to each: trusted sources, documented quality, compliant transport and a single point of accountability from load to delivery.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="reveal delay-1">
        <div class="corner-frame">
          <img src="/assets/industrial-port.jpg" alt="Aerial view of an industrial bulk commodities port at sunset" loading="lazy" width="1024" height="1024" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="stat-grid">
      <div class="stat-card reveal"><div class="stat-value">20+</div><div class="stat-label">Years Combined Experience</div></div>
